<section id="about" class="about section-padding">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 class="section-title font-display">About Worlds We Govern</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">
        Step into the heart of Singapore’s legislative process and into the
        shoes of a Member of Parliament. Worlds We Govern is a simulation series
        that seeks to democratise the policymaking experience for all!
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-content">
      <div class="wwg-description">
        <div class="side-header font-display">What is Worlds We Govern?</div>

        <div class="about-text">
          <p class="lead-text">
            <strong>Worlds We Govern</strong> is a simulation series that seeks to
            democratise the policymaking experience for all! From drafting bills to
            defending policies in parliamentary-style debates, this immersive experience
            challenges participants to navigate the nuances of Singapore’s legislative
            system and master the art of policymaking.
          </p>

          <p class="lead-text">
            Through our conference, we offer you a seat at the table to
            contribute ideas and opinions that build a more resilient and
            forward-looking Singapore, empowering them to bridge the gap between
            discourse and tangible impact.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="wwg-description">
      <div class="side-header font-display">Why Worlds We Govern?</div>

      <div class="about-text">
        <p class="lead-text">
          We serve as a platform that empowers participants to bridge the gap
          between discourse and tangible impact, taking the initiative to drive
          change within their own communities. This is exactly how strong and
          future-ready policymakers are built.
        </p>

        <p class="lead-text">
          We invite you to explore the conflicts, compromises, and convictions
          that shape our societies with us.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    background: linear-gradient(
      to bottom,
      #000000 0%,
      #1a0508 10%,
      #8b0000 30%,
      #8b0000 60%,
      #1a0508 90%,
      #000000 100%
    );
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 4vw, 1.25rem);
    color: var(--white);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .side-header {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    flex: 0 0 20%;
    align-self: center;
    text-align: left;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .about-content {
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
  }

  .wwg-description {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: clamp(1rem, 4vw, 6rem);
    width: 100%;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .about-background {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .about-bg-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center;
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .about-text {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 3;
    padding: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    border-radius: 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
    flex: 1;
  }

  .about-text p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 3vw, 1.125rem);
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--gray-700);
  }

  .lead-text {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 3vw, 1.25rem) !important;
    color: var(--gray-800) !important;
  }

  .initiative-section {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 1.5rem;
    padding: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid var(--gray-100);
  }

  .initiative-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .initiative-title {
    font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 3vw, 1.5rem);
    color: var(--gray-800);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .drafting-card {
    background: linear-gradient(
      135deg,
      var(--cream) 0%,
      rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.1) 100%
    );
    border-radius: 1rem;
    padding: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    border: 1px solid rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.2);
  }

  .card-title {
    font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 4vw, 1.75rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .card-text {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 3vw, 1.125rem);
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--gray-700);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .section-header {
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    .side-header {
      flex: 0 0 100%;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .wwg-description {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    .about-text {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .initiative-section {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .drafting-card {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .section-header {
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .about-text {
      padding: 1rem;
    }

    .about-text p {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .initiative-section {
      padding: 1rem;
    }

    .drafting-card {
      padding: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
